fc_o Port

Custom TAG_TYPE: TGC_O, Cycle Tag, Processor Function Code:

  • 1 - user data,
  • 2 - user program,
  • 5 - supervisor data : all exception vector entries except reset,
  • 6 - supervisor program : exception vector for reset,
  • 7 - cpu space: interrupt acknowledge.
